00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:22.000
Markaas waxaan ogaa dhacdooyinka

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:24.000
uu Quraanku sida joogtada u tilmaamayo,

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:26.000
Qaabkiisa ujeedka.

